Paper: hep-th/9307169

Date: 1993-07-28

Title: A Closed form for Consistent Anomalies in Gauge Theories

Authors: S. P. Sorella and L. Tataru

Comments: 18 pages, report REF. TUW. 93-15

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B324 (1994) 351-358

The new method for solving the descent equations for gauge theories proposedin \cite{s} is shown to be equivalent with that based on the {\em "Russianformula"}. Moreover it allows to obtain in a closed form the expressions of theconsistent anomalies in any space-time dimension.